name: We were going to be so happy in this house!
description:
It's not really a house, just a simple room. There's a table, a few chairs, a fireplace, a bed. If you want to sleep, you sleep on the bed. If you want to eat, you eat at the table. If you want to sit, you sit on the chairs. It's not really a house, but you could call it a house. It's the only thing here. No trees, no grass, no flowers. You might say it's a house, but it's not a house. It's just a room. It's the only thing here. And there's no one here.

A website. Made with CSS and GPT-3
